name: Skyking Dark - WebSDR utwenti & WebSDR.org
description:
A dark skin with mascot for websdr.ewi.utwente.nl:8901 and websdr.org. This style is an expansion of the one by 2E0PGS.

GitLab: https://gitlab.com/newstyledesu/websdr
additional_info:
10/13 - Unhid the header table and made it small and simpler to read with text. Hiding the header cleaned up and compacted the page, but it made some subpages, like Chirp Signal reception, work incorrectly. The mark up on this page is tricky because of the lack of and/or inconsistent selectors in some sections. 

10/8 - Content for the log tab styled to be more readable. Padding around the body reduced for cleanliness. The active state for mode buttons set to a red background to match tabs. 

9/24 - This theme now works properly on the list page webSDR.org (websdr.ewi.utwente.nl/org/) in addition to the regular site

9/24 - Changed the mascot to be full RGB rather than indexed/retro effect. Let me know if you like this style better.

9/24 - Changed the mascot to something that was more related. Also, I changed the image to base64 inline code. So, the theme will be a little bigger than before. If you like the old girl, you can get her here: https://a.pomf.space/jwkcfltvvlgz.png

9/23 - Fixed a problem where memories could not be labeled properly. 

9/23 - Changed the log tab background to be more readable; Changed the tab font to monospace; When the there is activity in the chat tab and it is out of focus, the color of the tab changes to something unreadable with white text. Therefore, I changed this to a dark rust color.

9/22 - Made hr elments have zero opacity. They have inline styles that help the layout so they can't be hidden.

9/22 - Fixed an error where the memories tab was hidden.

9/22 - Tested in modern FireFox and Chrome. Feel free to change the mascot by replacing the url on line 10.
